            "title": "碧湖花園三房443萬成交  持貨年升值63%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業表示，該行剛促成粉嶺碧湖花園3座中層A室，三房單位買賣成交，實用面積約489平方呎。單位近期叫價約445萬元，經議價後以443萬元成交，折合實用呎價約9,059元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主1994年6月以約271.04萬元購入上述單位，持貨近31年，是次轉手帳面獲利約171.96萬元，物業期間升值約63%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861926-%e7%a2%a7%e6%b9%96%e8%8a%b1%e5%9c%92%e4%b8%89%e6%88%bf443%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a8%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc63",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 15:15:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地A股午後陷爭持 滬指收升4點 深指跌0.16% 兩市成交不足萬億 金礦股回吐",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美關稅戰暗湧未平，內地A股午後陷爭持，滬深兩市總成交降至不足萬億；現貨金屢創新高後回吐，金礦股亦見調整。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/02899.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/02899.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開14點後，初段曾進一步試底，跌幅稍微擴大至跌17點、見3258點開始掉頭，早市全程反覆向上並於中段轉升，午後先呈好淡角力，其後一度發力升越早市高位，衝上3285點、升9點後又再掉頭，尾市曾倒跌；滬指最後收報3280點，升4點或0.13%，成交4425.97億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指略為跑輸，初段最低見9712點，跌62點，未幾已掉頭轉升，最高曾衝上9828點，升54點，午市大部份時間維持升市，但未再逼近早市高位，尾市更倒跌；深指收報9759點，跌15點或0.16%，成交5568.58億元。滬深兩市總成交僅9994.55億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌不足1點或0.02%，以3772點收市；創業板指數升1點或0.09%，報1908點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：山東黃金官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240712_FI_source-web_01787-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：山東黃金官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240712_FI_source-web_01787-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：山東黃金官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金礦股交投活躍，在滬深兩地A股市場成交額前15大榜上，均見到有關板塊股份的身影，股價則跌多升少。赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)跌3.67%，報28.85元；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)也跌0.22%，報31.64元；湖南黃金(002155.SZ)更跌4.7%。紫金礦業(02899)A股(601899.SH)則反覆微升0.45%，報17.82元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861896-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e9%99%b7%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%874%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c0-16-%e5%85%a9%e5%b8%82%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e4%b8%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 15:10:56",
